reviewText:
Hope this will help other gamers, have fun! ^.^

Costume Quest is a fun game, it's basically the grinch stole christmas but change the grinch with candy maniac skeleton monster and chrismas with halloween. you are playing as 2 siblings, later 1 of them together with friends, to save the other sibling who was kidnapped and posibly save haloween :)) you can equip diferent costumes for diferent abilities in turn based battles, as well as stamps to get bonuses;

Cons:
- short game;
- not really any replayability;

Pros:
- short game but fun;
- good variety of costume (thus abilities in combat + bonus from stamps);
- cute story + side story(afterstory i guess);
- not hard to 100%;
- nice medium sized world, but fun to explore;
- dialogue is so-so;
